headline: GTA Online
subtitle: New Till Death Do Us Part Maps, Double Cash 'Couples' Modes & More
content:
Love is in the air and it's raining down Double GTA$ & RP for all couples in Till Death Do Us Part, Hasta La Vista, Relay and Offense Defense. Till Death Do Us Part is back with two romantic new locations in Legion Square and La Puerta. Stick by each other for quicker health regen and remember to look out for your partner because if they die, so do you.

Check out the Rockstar Newswire for more details.
